article_id:572,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Facility Event, Flames of Reflection, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a846dca1aae981a566e2db2dea09d598.png,message:<div>A new facility event, Flames of Reflection, will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1562824800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the wind element. You&rsquo;ll also be able to build an event-related reward facility for your Halidom!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a846dca1aae981a566e2db2dea09d598.png"></div><div>Three sisters work together to forge weapons at the Halidom&#39;s smithy. There&#39;s Ramona, who is dependable and responsible, Rena, who is kind and calm, and Renee, who is cheerful and a bit of a dreamer.</div><div>Blacksmiths work behind the scenes to support the battles, but even they have a story! This is the heated tale of three women striving to reach greater heights as blacksmiths!</div><div><br></div><div>â–  Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1562824800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1563775199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1562738400,update_time1569489561